the angles of two plaquettes. Thus, if the action forbids plaquette angles
larger than $\pi$ and a single-link update is used, monopoles will be frozen 
and ergodicity will be lost.  {\em Right}: This problem
disappears, and ergodicity is restored, if {\em two} links are updated
simultaneously.
